post.description:
创建事件定义
```
  curl -X POST 'http://{host}:{port}/api/v3/horizon/v1/schema/event/create' \
    -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
    -H 'api-key: {apiKey}' \
    -H 'sensorsdata-project: {projectName}' \
    -d '{
    "physical_schema_name": "events",
    "schemas": [
      {
        "original_name": "buttonclick",
        "display_name": "buttonclick",
        "custom_params": {
          "meta_desc": "备注",
          "meta_trigger_action_desc": "aaa"
        },
        "statistics": {
          "track_platforms": [
            {
              "platform": "ANDROID",
              "has_data": false
            },
            {
              "platform": "IOS",
              "has_data": false
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
   }'
  返回值示例：
  {
    "code": "SUCCESS",
    "request_id": "1115555389cba16b5b816e0514fd338d",
    "data": {}
  }
```

批量创建属性
```
  curl -X POST 'http://{host}:{port}/api/v3/horizon/v1/schema/field/batch-create' \
    -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
    -H 'api-key: {api_key}' \
    -H 'sensorsdata-project: {projectName}' \
    -d '{
    "fields": [
      {
        "schema_name": "events",
        "field": {
          "name": "product_id",
          "display_name": "product_id",
          "data_type": {
            "type": "STRING"
          },
          "data_mapping": {
            "source_type": "MAIN_TABLE_COLUMN"
          },
          "custom_params": {
            "meta_desc": "备注"
          }
        }
      }
    ]
   }'
  返回值示例：
  {
    "code": "SUCCESS",
    "request_id": "11184302633b26d1accbe76da891b2f6",
    "data": {}
  }
```
 批量创建属性
 命名规则 `^[a-zA-Z_$][a-zA-Z\d_$]{0,99}$`
 不允许创建以下保留字段及包含保留前缀的字段
 - 保留字段
   - 公共保留字段
     - distinct_id, original_id, time, properties, id, first_id, second_id, users, events, event, user_id, date, datetime
   - SchemaClass = EVENT
     - 公共保留字段以及 event_id, event_bucket, day, week_id, month_id, _offset, sampling_group
   - SchemaClass = USER
     - 公共保留字段以及 _offset, first_id_type, second_id_type, generated_from, merged_to
   - SchemaClass = ITEM
     - 公共保留字段以及 item_type, item_id
 - 保留前缀
   - user_tag, user_group, $identity_, identity_, segment_ (可以创建 $ 开头的属性)

查询 Schema 关联的 Table
```
  curl -X POST 'http://{host}:{port}/api/v3/horizon/v1/schema/extended-table/list' \
    -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
    -H 'api-key: {api_key}' \
    -H 'sensorsdata-project: {projectName}' \
    -d '{
    "schema_names": ["events"]
  }'
  返回值示例：
  {
    "code": "SUCCESS",
    "request_id": "1210530786ea1e0e61e51918c5bbb3fd",
    "data": {
        "extended_tables": [
            {
                "extended_table_id": "users",
                "schema_name": "events",
                "db_name": "horizon_default_1",
                "table_name": "users",
                "table_display_type": "",
                "display_name": "users",
                "join_on_expression": "events.user_id = users.id",
                "join_key_columns": [
                    "id"
                ],
                "join_mode": "LEFT_JOIN"
            }
        ]
    }
  }
```

创建维度表关联关系，只能对物理 Schema 进行创建
```
  curl -X POST 'http://{host}:{port}/api/v3/horizon/v1/schema/extended-table/batch-create' \
    -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
    -H 'api-key: {api_key}' \
    -H 'sensorsdata-project: {projectName}' \
    -d '{
    "extended_tables": [
      {
        "extended_table_id": "test_table",
        "schema_name": "events",
        "db_name": "horizon_workspace_default_1",
        "table_name": "one_test_table",
        "display_name": "test_table",
        "join_on_expression": "events.video_id = one_test_table.id",
        "join_mode": "LEFT_JOIN"
      }
    ]
  }'
  返回值示例：
  {
    "code": "SUCCESS",
    "request_id": "121053078680124e06f58555ce009f333",
    "data": {
    }
  }
```

source_type.description:
属性来源类型
```
  FIELD_SOURCE_TYPE_UNSPECIFIED = 0;  // 表示 field 来自主表列，若单独使用时, 拼装方式为: SELECT ${source_column_name} AS ${view_column_name} FROM ${main_table}
  MAIN_TABLE_COLUMN = 1;              // 主表 表示 field 是扩展表的列，若单独使用时, 拼装方式为: SELECT ${source_column_name} AS ${view_column_name} FROM ${extended_table}
  EXTENDED_TABLE_COLUMN = 2;          // 使用表扩展属性，跨表计算出属性，原虚拟属性的逻辑, 例如: concat(events.aa, users.bb, items.cc)，均迁移到这个类型，官网文档: https://manual.sensorsdata.cn/sa/latest/%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7-22253764.html
  COMPLEX_EXPRESSION = 3;             // Schema 中多 Field 的计算， 暂不支持
  INLINE_EXPRESSION = 4;
```
